      <title>美国司法部加大力度避免选举混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部正在为 11 月的总统大选做准备，该部正在关注投票权斗争、调查威胁，并准备恢复与社交媒体公司的简报，以遏制错误信息的传播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
